snippet: Democratic and labor groups have been major players in the race, but Gov. Scott Walker has spent the most money, partly as a result of a state law that exempted him from contribution limits until the recall election was formally announced in March.
lead_paragraph: Democratic and labor groups have been major players in the race, but Gov. Scott Walker has spent the most money, partly as a result of a state law that exempted him from contribution limits until the recall election was formally announced in March.
